Hey 0x00sec people! Not long ago, I said I would put up some source code for Dijkstra's Algorithm. Today, I'll be showing you just _one_ way to do it. We'll be utilizing an **Adjacency Matrix**, which is simply a 2D Array. _As we progress, each implementation will be more efficient than the last._

